      "title": "Hello World",
      "blocks": [
        {
          "type": "text",
          "id": "block-hello-intro",
          "position": { "order": 0 },
          "style": { "spacing": "md", "alignment": "left" },
          "content": {
            "format": "markdown",
            "value": "## 你的第一个程序\n\n每个程序员学习新语言时，第一个程序都是输出 \"Hello, World!\"。\n\n在 Python 中，我们使用 `print()` 函数来输出内容。"
          }
        },
        {
          "type": "codeBlock",
          "id": "block-hello-example",
          "position": { "order": 1 },
          "style": { "spacing": "md", "alignment": "left" },
          "content": {
            "language": "python",
            "code": "print(\"Hello, World!\")"
          }
        },
        {
          "type": "text",
          "id": "block-try-it",
          "position": { "order": 2 },
          "style": { "spacing": "sm", "alignment": "left" },
          "content": {
            "format": "markdown",
            "value": "### 动手试试\n\n点击下方的「运行」按钮，看看会发生什么："
          }
        },
        {
          "type": "codePlayground",
          "id": "block-hello-playground",
          "position": { "order": 3 },
          "style": { "spacing": "md", "alignment": "left" },
          "content": {
            "language": "python",
            "initialCode": "# 点击运行按钮，执行这段代码\nprint(\"Hello, World!\")",
            "expectedOutput": "Hello, World!",
            "hints": ["直接点击运行按钮即可"],
            "runnable": true
          }
        },
        {
          "type": "multipleChoice",
          "id": "block-hello-quiz",
          "position": { "order": 4 },
          "style": { "spacing": "md", "alignment": "left" },
          "content": {
            "question": "print() 函数的作用是什么？",
            "options": [
              { "id": "a", "text": "将内容输出到屏幕" },
              { "id": "b", "text": "读取用户输入" },
              { "id": "c", "text": "定义一个变量" },
              { "id": "d", "text": "进行数学计算" }
            ],
            "correctAnswer": "a",
            "explanation": "print() 函数用于将括号内的内容输出到屏幕（控制台）。这是 Python 中最常用的函数之一。",
            "multiSelect": false
          }
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "pageId": "page-variables",
      "title": "变量",
      "blocks": [
        {
          "type": "text",
          "id": "block-var-intro",
          "position": { "order": 0 },
          "style": { "spacing": "md", "alignment": "left" },
          "content": {
            "format": "markdown",
            "value": "## 什么是变量？\n\n变量就像一个**盒子**，可以用来存储数据。\n\n你可以给这个盒子起一个名字，然后把数据放进去。"
          }
        },
        {
          "type": "codeBlock",
          "id": "block-var-example",
          "position": { "order": 1 },
          "style": { "spacing": "md", "alignment": "left" },
          "content": {
            "language": "python",
            "code": "# 创建变量\nname = \"小明\"    # 字符串类型\nage = 18        # 整数类型\nheight = 1.75   # 浮点数类型\n\n# 输出变量\nprint(name)\nprint(age)\nprint(height)"
          }
        },
        {
          "type": "text",
          "id": "block-var-rules",
          "position": { "order": 2 },
          "style": { "spacing": "md", "alignment": "left" },
          "content": {
            "format": "markdown",
            "value": "### 变量命名规则\n\n1. 只能包含字母、数字和下划线 `_`\n2. 不能以数字开头\n3. 区分大小写（`name` 和 `Name` 是不同的变量）\n4. 不能使用 Python 关键字（如 `if`、`for`、`print` 等）"
          }
        },
        {
          "type": "codePlayground",
          "id": "block-var-practice",
          "position": { "order": 3 },
          "style": { "spacing": "md", "alignment": "left" },
          "content": {
            "language": "python",
            "initialCode": "# 练习：创建一个变量 x，值为 10，然后输出它\n# 在下面写你的代码：\n\n",
            "expectedOutput": "10",
            "hints": [
              "第一步：x = 10",
              "第二步：print(x)",
              "完整答案：\nx = 10\nprint(x)"
            ],
            "runnable": true
          }
        },
        {
          "type": "fillBlank",
          "id": "block-var-fill",
          "position": { "order": 4 },
          "style": { "spacing": "md", "alignment": "left" },
          "content": {
            "question": "在 Python 中，使用 ______ 符号给变量赋值",
            "correctAnswer": "=",
            "hint": "这是一个等号，不是双等号"
          }
        }
      ]
    },
